{"type":"message","id":"a42b597b","parentId":"c9a677d6","timestamp":"2026-03-03T06:18:10.576Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_vmx8xf84kbvu_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\n  \"query\": \"China A-share stock real-time price data API\",\n  \"total\": 10,\n  \"results\": [\n    {\n      \"tool_id\": \"eodhd.live_prices.retrieve.v1.178541d4\",\n      \"name\": \"Live (Delayed) Stock Prices\",\n      \"description\": \"Retrieve live or delayed stock prices and macroeconomic data.\",\n      \"params\": [\n        {\n          \"name\": \"ticker\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": true,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"Ticker symbol with exchange suffix (e.g., AAPL.US).\"\n          }\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"s\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"Optional filter parameter.\"\n          }\n        }\n      ],\n      \"examples\": {\n        \"sample_parameters\": {\n          \"ticker\": \"AAPL.US\"\n        }\n      },\n      \"provider_description\": \"Access historical end-of-day stock prices, intraday data, US stock options, and real-time prices with free and advanced plans. EODHD provides financial data for 150,000+ tickers, including stocks, ETFs, funds, and currencies worldwide.\",\n      \"stats\": {\n        \"avg_execution_time_ms\": 1248.29,\n        \"success_rate\": 0.938\n      }\n    },\n    {\n      \"tool_id\": \"ths_ifind.real_time_quotation.v1\",\n      \"name\": \"iFinD 同花顺实时行情 (THS Real-time Quotation)\",\n      \"description\": \"Query real-time quotation data for securities in the 同花顺 (THS) iFinD database, providing real-time market data for financial products including stocks, funds, bonds, and futures, such as real-time prices, trading volumes, price changes, bid/ask quotes, etc. Supports querying various real-time indicators including latest price, price change, trading volume, turnover ratio, market value, and five-level bid/ask quotes.\",\n      \"params\": [\n        {\n          \"name\": \"codes\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": true,\n          \"description\": \"Security codes, multiple codes separated by commas (max 50), e.g., '300033.SZ,600030.SH'\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"indicators\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": \"Indicator list, multiple indicators separated by commas. Options: 'common' (common indicators), 'all' (all indicators), or custom indicator list. Default is 'all'\"\n        }\n      ],\n      \"examples\": {\n        \"sample_parameters\": {\n          \"codes\": \"300033.SZ,600030.SH\"\n        }\n      },\n      \"provider_description\": \"同花顺 (THS) iFinD data provider, offering financial data for Chinese and international markets including stocks, securities, funds, bonds, futures, etc. Supports company announcements, intelligent stock screening, industry analysis, market trend prediction, and more, helping users conduct comprehensive financial data analysis and investment decisions.\",\n      \"stats\": {\n        \"avg_execution_time_ms\": 0,\n        \"success_rate\": 1\n      }\n    },\n    {\n      \"tool_id\": \"eodhd.real_time.retrieve.v1.3b8a5cf8\",\n      \"name\": \"Retrieve Real-Time (Delayed) Stock Prices\",\n      \"description\": \"Fetch real-time price data for a specified cryptocurrency pair.\",\n      \"params\": [\n        {\n          \"name\": \"symbol\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": true,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"Stock ticker symbol with exchange suffix (e.g., AAPL.US)\"\n          }\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"fmt\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"Response format\"\n          },\n          \"enum\": [\n            \"json\",\n            \"csv\"\n          ]\n        }\n      ],\n      \"examples\": {\n        \"sample_parameters\": {\n          \"symbol\": \"EUR.FOREX\"\n        }\n      },\n      \"provider_description\": \"Access historical end-of-day stock prices, intraday data, US stock options, and real-time prices with free and advanced plans. EODHD provides financial data for 150,000+ tickers, including stocks, ETFs, funds, and currencies worldwide.\",\n      \"stats\": {\n        \"avg_execution_time_ms\": 1154.75,\n        \"success_rate\": 0.867\n      }\n    },\n    {\n      \"tool_id\": \"financial_modeling_prep.stock.quote.retrieve.v1.822497ca\",\n      \"name\": \"Stock Quote API\",\n      \"description\": \"Access real-time stock quotes with the FMP Stock Quote API. Get up-to-the-minute prices, changes, and volume data for individual stocks. Also access real-time stock index quotes, stay updated with the latest price changes, daily highs and lows, volume, and other key metrics for major stock indices around the world. This API can also be used for commodities, forex, and cryptocurrencies.\",\n      \"params\": [\n        {\n          \"name\": \"symbol\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": true,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"Symbol for the asset\"\n          }\n        }\n      ],\n      \"examples\": {\n        \"sample_parameters\": {\n          \"symbol\": \"AAPL\"\n        }\n      },\n      \"provider_description\": \"Financial Modeling Prep is a financial data platform that provides real-time and historical stock market data, financial statements, company profiles, and other financial metrics for public companies, private companies, and ETFs.\",\n      \"stats\": {\n        \"avg_execution_time_ms\": 994.08,\n        \"success_rate\": 0.113\n      }\n    },\n    {\n      \"tool_id\": \"financial_modeling_prep.historical_price_eod.full.retrieve.v1.b0c32b22\",\n      \"name\": \"Detailed Historical Price Data\",\n      \"description\": \"Access full price and volume data for any stock symbol using the FMP Comprehensive Stock Price and Volume Data API. Get detailed insights, including open, high, low, close prices, trading volume, price changes, percentage changes, and volume-weighted average price (VWAP).; Access stock price and volume data without adjustments for stock splits with the FMP Unadjusted Stock Price Chart API. Get accurate insights into stock performance, including open, high, low, and close prices, along with trading volume, without split-related changes.; Access full historical end-of-day prices for stock indexes using the Detailed Historical Price Data API. This API provides comprehensive information, including open, high, low, close prices, volume, and additional metrics for detailed financial analysis. Also used for commodities, forex, cryptocurrencies.\",\n      \"params\": [\n        {\n          \"name\": \"symbol\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": true,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"Symbol for the asset\"\n          }\n        }\n      ],\n      \"examples\": {\n        \"sample_parameters\": {\n          \"symbol\": \"AAPL\"\n        }\n      },\n      \"provider_description\": \"Financial Modeling Prep is a financial data platform that provides real-time and historical stock market data, financial statements, company profiles, and other financial metrics for public companies, private companies, and ETFs.\",\n      \"stats\": {\n        \"avg_execution_time_ms\": 1218.95,\n        \"success_rate\": 0.001\n      }\n    },\n    {\n      \"tool_id\": \"financial_modeling_prep.quote_short.retrieve.v1.729a84c2\",\n      \"name\": \"Stock Index Short Quote\",\n      \"description\": \"Get quick snapshots of real-time stock quotes with the FMP Stock Quote Short API. Access key stock data like current price, volume, and price changes for instant market insights.; Access concise stock index quotes with the Stock Index Short Quote API. This API provides a snapshot of the current price, change, and volume for stock indexes, making it ideal for users who need a quick overview of market movements. Also used for commodities, forex, cryptocurrencies.\",\n      \"params\": [\n        {\n          \"name\": \"symbol\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": true,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"Symbol for the asset\"\n          }\n        }\n      ],\n      \"examples\": {\n        \"sample_parameters\": {\n          \"symbol\": \"^GSPC\"\n        }\n      },\n      \"provider_description\": \"Financial Modeling Prep is a financial data platform that provides real-time and historical stock market data, financial statements, company profiles, and other financial metrics for public companies, private companies, and ETFs.\",\n      \"stats\": {\n        \"avg_execution_time_ms\": 1197.39,\n        \"success_rate\": 0.202\n      }\n    },\n    {\n      \"tool_id\": \"financial_modeling_prep.stock.price.change.retrieve.v1.70c8c8d6\",\n      \"name\": \"Stock Price Change API\",\n      \"description\": \"Track stock price fluctuations in real-time with the FMP Stock Price Change API. Monitor percentage and value changes over various time periods, including daily, weekly, monthly, and long-term.\",\n      \"params\": [\n        {\n          \"name\": \"symbol\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": true,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"Stock symbol\"\n          }\n        }\n      ],\n      \"examples\": {\n        \"sample_parameters\": {\n          \"symbol\": \"AAPL\"\n        }\n      },\n      \"provider_description\": \"Financial Modeling Prep is a financial data platform that provides real-time and historical stock market data, financial statements, company profiles, and other financial metrics for public companies, private companies, and ETFs.\",\n      \"stats\": {\n        \"avg_execution_time_ms\": 1031.65,\n        \"success_rate\": 0.282\n      }\n    },\n    {\n      \"tool_id\": \"finnhub_io_api.stock.quote\",\n      \"name\": \"Quote\",\n      \"description\": \"Get real-time quote data for US stocks.\",\n      \"params\": [\n        {\n          \"name\": \"symbol\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": true,\n          \"description\": \"Stock symbol\"\n        }\n      ],\n      \"examples\": {\n        \"sample_parameters\": {\n          \"symbol\": \"AAPL\"\n        }\n      },\n      \"provider_description\": \"Finnhub - Free APIs for realtime stock, forex, and cryptocurrency. Company fundamentals, Economic data, and Alternative data.\",\n      \"stats\": {\n        \"avg_execution_time_ms\": 3.472,\n        \"success_rate\": 1\n      }\n    },\n    {\n      \"tool_id\": \"ths_ifind.hk_connect_stats.v1\",\n      \"name\": \"iFinD 沪深港通交易统计 (HK Stock Connect Trading Stats)\",\n      \"description\": \"Query Shanghai-Shenzhen-Hong Kong Stock Connect trading statistics from 同花顺 (THS) iFinD database. Covers northbound (沪股通, 深股通) and southbound (港股通沪市, 港股通深市) channels. Returns trading volume, buy/sell amounts, net buy amount, transaction counts, and top-10 active stocks concentration ratios. Supports daily, weekly, monthly, and yearly aggregation. Useful for tracking cross-border capital flows between mainland China and Hong Kong markets.\",\n      \"params\": [\n        {\n          \"name\": \"sdate\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": true,\n          \"description\": \"Start date. Supported formats: 'YYYY-MM-DD', 'YYYY/MM/DD', 'YYYYMMDD'.\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"edate\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": true,\n          \"description\": \"End date. Supported formats: 'YYYY-MM-DD', 'YYYY/MM/DD', 'YYYYMMDD'.\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"zq\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": \"Aggregation period. Valid values: 'day', 'week', 'month', 'year'. Defaults to 'week'.\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"lx\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": \"Channel type filter. 'ALL'=all channels, '1'=沪股通, '2'=港股通(沪市), '3'=深股通, '4'=港股通(深市). Defaults to 'ALL'.\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"bz\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": \"Currency for amounts. Defaults to 'CNY'.\"\n        }\n      ],\n      \"provider_description\": \"同花顺 (THS) iFinD data provider, offering financial data for Chinese and international markets including stocks, securities, funds, bonds, futures, etc. Supports company announcements, intelligent stock screening, industry analysis, market trend prediction, and more, helping users conduct comprehensive financial data analysis and investment decisions.\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"tool_id\": \"financialmodelingprep.historical_price_eod.non_split_adjusted.retrieve.v1.4c43e8ed\",\n      \"name\": \"Retrieve Non-Split-Adjusted Historical Price Data\",\n      \"description\": \"Access stock price and volume data without adjustments for stock splits with the FMP Unadjusted Stock Price Chart API. Get accurate insights into stock performance, including open, high, low, and close prices, along with trading volume, without split-related changes.\",\n      \"params\": [\n        {\n          \"name\": \"symbol\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": true,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"Stock symbol\"\n          }\n        }\n      ],\n      \"examples\": {\n        \"sample_parameters\": {\n          \"symbol\": \"AAPL\"\n        }\n      },\n      \"provider_description\": \"FMP offers a stock market data API covers real-time stock prices, historical prices and market news to stock fundamentals and company information. We provide one of the most accurate financial data available on the market. You can get historical prices, fundamental data, insider transactions, and much more that goes back 30 years in history.\",\n      \"stats\": {\n        \"avg_execution_time_ms\": 1.255,\n        \"success_rate\": 1\n      }\n    }\n  ],\n  \"search_id\": \"9dc2047c-7428-4c87-b7e4-5228c278a353\",\n  \"elapsed_time_ms\": 659.84\n}"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":5041,"aggregated":"{\n  \"query\": \"China A-share stock real-time price data API\",\n  \"total\": 10,\n  \"results\": [\n    {\n      \"tool_id\": \"eodhd.live_prices.retrieve.v1.178541d4\",\n      \"name\": \"Live (Delayed) Stock Prices\",\n      \"description\": \"Retrieve live or delayed stock prices and macroeconomic data.\",\n      \"params\": [\n        {\n          \"name\": \"ticker\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": true,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"Ticker symbol with exchange suffix (e.g., AAPL.US).\"\n          }\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"s\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"Optional filter parameter.\"\n          }\n        }\n      ],\n      \"examples\": {\n        \"sample_parameters\": {\n          \"ticker\": \"AAPL.US\"\n        }\n      },\n      \"provider_description\": \"Access historical end-of-day stock prices, intraday data, US stock options, and real-time prices with free and advanced plans. EODHD provides financial data for 150,000+ tickers, including stocks, ETFs, funds, and currencies worldwide.\",\n      \"stats\": {\n        \"avg_execution_time_ms\": 1248.29,\n        \"success_rate\": 0.938\n      }\n    },\n    {\n      \"tool_id\": \"ths_ifind.real_time_quotation.v1\",\n      \"name\": \"iFinD 同花顺实时行情 (THS Real-time Quotation)\",\n      \"description\": \"Query real-time quotation data for securities in the 同花顺 (THS) iFinD database, provid